Charlayne Woodard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlayne_Woodard 0 Charlaine "Charlayne" Woodard (born December 29, 1953) is an American film, stage, and television actress and playwright. She has written four plays, titled Pretty Fire, Neat, In Real Life, which she starred in, and Flight.
